00:12:18.760 --> 00:12:23.490
If you have two notifications
that would otherwise be

00:12:23.490 --> 00:12:27.720
displayed on top of one another,
the basic rule of

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:31.610
thumb is that your app should
never appear more than once in

00:12:31.610 --> 00:12:32.510
the notification panel.

00:12:32.510 --> 00:12:37.060
So if you have something new
to say, then say it inside

00:12:37.060 --> 00:12:40.030
your existing notification,
rather than creating a second

00:12:40.030 --> 00:12:40.970
notification.

00:12:40.970 --> 00:12:43.950
For instance, you could add a
number pending field to let

00:12:43.950 --> 00:12:46.350
